								<p><span>Welcome to the fifth edition of The Rising Clyde, a newsletter from the COP26 Coalition! Just a reminder to send us any resources, articles and random things from the climate movement </span><a href="https://forms.gle/Ukd1WiWVKPMUmD8M8"><span>here</span></a><span>! Also, remember to join our </span><a href="https://calendar.google.com/calendar/b/2?cid=Y29wMjZjb2FsaXRpb251a0ByaXNldXAubmV0"><span>shared calendar</span></a><span> to make it easier to find the dates and details for upcoming meetings and events. For now, </span><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6nZQRt4BXr8"><span>click here for the Soundtrack for #5</span></a><span> and enjoy your pre-2nd-lockdown read! </span></p>
